PrecisRegulations Amending the REGULATIONS PRESCRIBING EXCLUSIONS FROM CERTAIN DEFINITIONS OF THE CRIMINAL CODE (INTERNATIONAL SPORTING COMPETITION HANDGUNS) which add a number of handguns used in international shooting competitions to the list of handguns that are excluded from the Criminal Code definition of "prohibited firearms".
